Text: Documentsis the latest version of the contract which just went out to the customer The next step is a negotiations meeting scheduled for this Thursday Our objective is still a close early next week Cheers Harald Forwarded by Harald JensenHOUEES on PM Enron Energy Services From Mike D Smith PM To cc Laurie ES Harald ES Angela ES Subject Documents Attached you will find the master agreement and the confirmation for the CA facilities I have marked in red provisions that we have added or deleted based upon our conversation last week and your subsequent comments We will need to discuss further with you any comments that you have given that we have not addressed in this draft We look forward to meeting with you on Thurs MDS
